race.comment: SUNSET DIABLO (3) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Finished second (27.73) at this track last time making it two minors on end. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Well placed and gets his chance. BORN TO PARTY (1) stuck on well last time to finish a neck back in second (27.74) at this track in a Novice race over 488m. Will give a great sight again. SUNSET PARIS (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a third place finish (28.01) there the start prior. Has ability and is one of the better chances. MY MOET (5) did a good job to finish third last time out over 400m at this track (22.72) in a Novice race, the second top-three finish on the trot.
